  <body>
        <h1> Rent a Book or Movie </h1>

        <h4> Instructions </h4>

        <ol> 
            <li> Select the type of media you would like to rent. Please keep in mind, you may only rent 
                the type of media your account is registered for. Please be prepared with the title, author, 
                and OL number for a book rental, or the title, IMDB ID, and release year for a movie. If you 
                are unaware of any of this information please use the <a href = "/search">media search</a> to determine this.</li>
            <li> Once you select the type of media you would like and press submit, the next page will be where you include your username, password, and media info.
                 Enter the information necessary and click the rent button. If your item was unsucessfully rented you will reveive an error message. </li>
        </ol>
        <h4> What would you like to rent? </h4>

        <form action="/rentMedia" method="get">
        <label><input type="radio" name="mediaType" value="Books" required>Book</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="mediaType" value="Movies" required>Movie</label>
        <br>
        <br>
        <input id="button" type="submit"> 
        </form>
        <br>

        <span class="material-symbols-outlined"><a href="/">home</a></span>

  </body>

